\title{Reflexive relation}
\author{alex-nelson}
\import{notation}
\date{2025-12-09}
\taxon{definition}
\meta{source}{[[paul-r-halmos]] [[halmos-1974-naive]] Ch.7}
\MML{relat_2}{def 9}{V1}

\p{Let #{R} be a relation, let #{F} be its [field](nst-000X). We say #{R} is \define{Reflexive} if for each #{x\in F} we have #{(x,x)\in R}.}